   "source": [
    "# 5.1 python中的序列分类\n",
    "\n",
    "序列是 python 中重要的协议\n",
    "\n",
    "按照元素类型是否相同\n",
    "\n",
    "容器序列：list、tuple、deque\n",
    "\n",
    "扁平序列：str、bytes、bytearray、array.array\n",
    "\n",
    "按照元素是否可变\n",
    "\n",
    "可变类型：list、deque、bytearray、array.array\n",
    "\n",
    "不可变：str、tuple、bytes"
